      <p></p>
<p>Losing a friend leaves a void that’s hard to fill.  These messages offer solace and understanding to friends during their time of sorrow.</p>
<li>I am so sorry for your loss. My heart aches for you.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and sending all my love.</li>
<li>I’ll always cherish the memories we shared with [deceased's name].</li>
<li>Your friendship means so much to me, and I’m here for you.</li>
<li>I can't imagine what you're going through, but please know I'm here.</li>
<li>Sending strength and love your way.</li>
<li>Please accept my deepest sympathies.</li>
<li>I’m so saddened by the news of [deceased's name]'s passing.</li>
<li>May beautiful memories ease your sorrow.</li>
<li>Know that you are not alone in your grief.</li>
<li>Holding you in my heart during this difficult time.</li>
<li>I will always remember [deceased's name]'s [positive quality].</li>
<li>My thoughts are with you.</li>
